  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The world around Hungry Joe's Pizza's may have changed, but nothing is going to get in the way of delivering his loyal customers their pies.</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As the latest employee, your job is to make and deliver the same classic pizzas Joe's has been serving to customers for decades. <i>Just don't ask what happened to the last delivery driver.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382660/extras/5de98ddae1e2d279b9bad790e0e53d89.poster.avif?t=1738708881\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382660/extras/5de98ddae1e2d279b9bad790e0e53d89.webm?t=1738708881\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382660/extras/5de98ddae1e2d279b9bad790e0e53d89.mp4?t=1738708881\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Inspired by old flash games and the retro era of 3D, <strong>Pizza Blitz</strong> is a split between a chill cooking simulator where you make pizzas and <i>vibe</i>, and a hectic score-attack driving game where you must deliver your pizzas in a city under fire.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382660/extras/3b7f4740473cb2a59d506b93cb05fd85.poster.avif?t=1738708881\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382660/extras/3b7f4740473cb2a59d506b93cb05fd85.webm?t=1738708881\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382660/extras/3b7f4740473cb2a59d506b93cb05fd85.mp4?t=1738708881\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Originally a jam game made for <i>Brackey's Game Jam 2024.2</i>, it has now been expanded upon and streamlined to be a more <strong>complete</strong> experience.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Complete your 5 day work week, each with a pizza making and delivery section</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Combine ingredients to craft 11 different  pizza recipes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Intense, fast paced delivery gameplay with <i>sleek</i> driving controls and dopamine inducing drifting</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Score high points to buy various useful and, really not so useful items for the pizzeria</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >18 unique achievements</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The world around Hungry Joe's Pizza's may have changed, but nothing is going to get in the way of delivering his loyal customers their pies.</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As the latest employee, your job is to make and deliver the same classic pizzas Joe's has been serving to customers for decades. <i>Just don't ask what happened to the last delivery driver.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382660/extras/5de98ddae1e2d279b9bad790e0e53d89.poster.avif?t=1738708881\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382660/extras/5de98ddae1e2d279b9bad790e0e53d89.webm?t=1738708881\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382660/extras/5de98ddae1e2d279b9bad790e0e53d89.mp4?t=1738708881\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Inspired by old flash games and the retro era of 3D, <strong>Pizza Blitz</strong> is a split between a chill cooking simulator where you make pizzas and <i>vibe</i>, and a hectic score-attack driving game where you must deliver your pizzas in a city under fire.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382660/extras/3b7f4740473cb2a59d506b93cb05fd85.poster.avif?t=1738708881\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382660/extras/3b7f4740473cb2a59d506b93cb05fd85.webm?t=1738708881\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382660/extras/3b7f4740473cb2a59d506b93cb05fd85.mp4?t=1738708881\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Originally a jam game made for <i>Brackey's Game Jam 2024.2</i>, it has now been expanded upon and streamlined to be a more <strong>complete</strong> experience.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Complete your 5 day work week, each with a pizza making and delivery section</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Combine ingredients to craft 11 different  pizza recipes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Intense, fast paced delivery gameplay with <i>sleek</i> driving controls and dopamine inducing drifting</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Score high points to buy various useful and, really not so useful items for the pizzeria</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >18 unique achievements</p></li></ul>",
